Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.85,sign_0_1_Coffee_Shop,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Coffee Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.32,0:00:04.40,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.87,0:00:08.86,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The script for the Hitotose Troupe's \Nfirst performance is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.16,0:00:12.40,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:13.91,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.91,0:00:15.05,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:17.28,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,And Mayu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:18.37,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:25.88,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:27.66,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.66,0:00:31.20,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The ending might change, depending \Non how the production works out,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:33.69,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,but that's the general idea \Nthat I want to go with.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.69,0:00:35.51,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:42.13,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,For this part...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:44.02,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:46.65,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You look really happy, Mayu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.52,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now that the story's \Ncome together, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:53.48,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,...we can start trying on costumes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:32.00,sign_3525_20_Pa_Pa_Parade,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Pa-Pa-Parade
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:34.75,sign_3645_21_Coffee_Shop_Hito,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Used Bookstore Hitotose
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:38.01,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I went out and got the perfect \Ncostumes for each of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:40.74,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to see you try them on right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:43.57,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You're in quite the rush, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:46.05,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,When do most troupes do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:48.28,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Right before the show, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:50.42,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,They call it the "parade."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:51.65,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Parade?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:57.40,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Not that kind of parade!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.03,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:02.13,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,The "dress parade" is when
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:03.97,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,the actors line up with their costumes on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:06.04,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,to check everything over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:09.97,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,So it can't really be done \Nuntil right before the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:10.68,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:14.10,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,There are some things you can't check on \Nuntil you've basically finished all rehearsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:15.04,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:16.67,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,No way! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:19.84,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play with all of you \Nin cute costumes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.05,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:23.62,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,She's reverted to a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:26.18,Main Dialogue Top,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I want to! I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:26.81,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to do it that badly, \NI guess we'll have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:30.31,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:34.94,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:34.94,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:39.69,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I don't usually wear stuff \Nlike this, so it's new to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:43.70,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You don't work in the coffee shop at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:46.08,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I helped out once,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:49.63,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,but it was too hard to resist \Nthe urge to sneak bites.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:52.46,sign_5511_51_Staaaaare,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Staaaaare
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:52.46,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:56.84,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, skirts just feel too weird on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.06,0:03:59.65,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Really? But it looks so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:03.09,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,But it's so loose and billowy, \Nit's hard to move around in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:06.13,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I can't run off at full speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:10.98,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you'll have many opportunities \Nto run at full speed in the shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:14.82,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, you've been helping out \Nin the coffee shop a lot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:16.75,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Are you used to wearing maid uniforms?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:20.61,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It doesn't embarrass me \Nas much as it used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:23.57,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I got this one \Nfor you, Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:28.48,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:30.62,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,She's a bunny girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:36.13,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... That's really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:38.71,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, you look sexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:41.63,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a little too revealing, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:46.64,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:49.35,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to think of it \Nas the coffee shop's uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.52,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you forcing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:56.02,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:59.25,Main Dialogue,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Yua-chan would\N look cute in an apron dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:02.53,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, I look cute in anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:06.18,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,When we stand together like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.09,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you really stand out, Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:08.97,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:09.97,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:11.76,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:15.04,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,When we put Hina-chan and \NYua-chan together...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:16.40,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:18.98,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They look like they're from \N{\i1}Alice in Wonderland,{\i0} don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:21.21,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:24.17,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't seem much like \Na fairy tale to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:28.65,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Alice and the rabbit, huh? I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:31.72,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,That just leaves...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.50,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:39.19,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aki-chan has such a nice figure, \Nit was hard to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:37.57,Main Dialogue Top,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That looks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:39.19,Main Dialogue Top,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:43.38,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Something like this could work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.18,0:05:45.30,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Rawr.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:48.01,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Or even this, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:51.70,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,They're all so cute, I can't choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:55.33,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,None of those are even \Nin the script, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.21,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:58.88,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Also, also...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:02.71,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I think something like this will look good \Non Hina-chan and Aki-chan, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:09.25,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, those are basically just underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:12.97,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I think they're really \Nfrilly and cute, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:16.00,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan's out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:17.98,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,She's taking this way too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:22.50,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But if these costumes \Nwill make our show better...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:24.19,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you go that far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:27.24,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Do you actually {\i1}want{\i0} to wear that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:29.49,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:32.37,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:36.85,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,My mom is coming to visit \NHitotose Manor soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:38.00,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:41.39,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted her to see our first performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:46.70,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to put on a good show \Nand put her mind at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:50.13,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry it's such a selfish reason, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:54.78,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,We can't show Hina-chan's mom a messy shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:58.52,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I have to clean up, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:01.44,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a certain way \Nyour mom likes her meals flavored?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:03.56,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start practicing it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:07.33,Main Dialogue,Aki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we should wax the floors?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:08.28,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:10.15,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get brand new bookshelves, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:13.41,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,While we're at it, should we \Nremodel the kitchen, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:15.78,Main Dialogue,Aki,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should change the wallpaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:19.54,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You guys need to put all that effort\N toward rehearsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:21.79,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.17,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told us that earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.79,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:30.89,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,We're all partners in the Hitotose Troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:32.62,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:34.07,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:35.92,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it all to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.92,0:07:39.87,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put on a great performance, \Nfor Hina-chan's mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:40.64,Main Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:45.79,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:52.29,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Now that that's all worked out,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:54.82,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,why don't we have a toast?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:57.43,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,And we can have a snack while we're at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:02.70,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little early, but \Nwhy don't we have dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:04.33,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:08.13,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.34,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:13.34,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, who's going to do the toast?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:17.50,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:22.40,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I think the Hitotose Troupe's principal,\N Hina-chan, should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:24.23,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.47,0:08:26.16,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:27.73,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,We've all got our drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:30.86,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:32.89,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:34.90,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:41.50,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,To the success of the \NHitotose Troupe's first performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:43.43,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:45.62,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.63,Note,Text,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to study Japanese!\NOr so I thought when I did my test\Nand got an awful score! {\c&HBA2FE3&}(I really did it now)\N\N{\c&H7C6055&}I'm sure they'll want to see my score when I get home...\N...To think that I got that score in Japanese...\N...What am I supposed to tell my mom?\NI'll just keep it a secret until my science test comes back, since I'm good at that...\N{\c&HBA2FE3&}It'll be okay... It'll be okay... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:50.13,sign_12651_151_Coffee_Shop,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Coffee Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:54.01,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,That looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:54.91,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:56.56,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:57.89,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:01.89,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you having a costume party\N today or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:03.83,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,No, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:07.36,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I came because I heard you \Nhad finished the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:11.40,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, so we were having a bit \Nof an early dress parade...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:14.63,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, would you like to wear one, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:17.41,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan's switch \Njust got flipped on again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.93,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the route you're taking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:26.19,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I've been hoping to ask for your\Nadvice since I started writing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:29.65,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we do have limited stage space.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:32.67,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,This has been such a fulfilling day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:37.04,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,There's still one costume left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:38.92,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lovely dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:41.31,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, like one a princess would wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:45.22,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:46.18,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:49.07,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Since we have this, why don't you try it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:49.85,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:53.44,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You did say you wanted to be a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:54.42,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:56.32,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like it's just your size.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.35,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:10:00.07,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.25,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute, Mayu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:12.02,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It looks great on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:13.70,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,It's like it was made-to-order!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:16.11,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You really do look like a princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:22.22,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Argh! I feel so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:25.80,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.38,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It suits you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.19,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:33.40,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we do a reading right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.80,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:39.25,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,We only have a few weeks \Nuntil the performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:42.57,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to waste a single second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.78,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,But if we start now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:47.16,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,it might get too late \Nfor you to get back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:50.07,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:51.92,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I came prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:11:01.16,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You had every intention of \Nspending the night here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:04.05,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is Sunday, which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:06.56,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,An impromptu training camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:09.91,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,That's very sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:12.88,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, all you change into your pajamas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:14.19,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:17.12,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,This play takes place in a dream land,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.12,0:11:18.77,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,a wonderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:22.57,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think pajamas would be \Nthe best costume to set the mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:26.57,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that's not a "dream land."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:28.20,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's a "wonderland."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:32.34,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds kind of interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:34.36,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go change right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:39.33,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,A pajama party...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.89,0:11:45.12,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Ruri-chan really \Ndoes like this sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:45.92,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:50.56,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't bring pajamas or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:53.98,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:56.40,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You can borrow my pajamas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:12:00.86,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I have some very nice, grown-up ones \Nthat would be perfect for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:10.25,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:13.25,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You look just like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:14.50,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You're not kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:15.04,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.00,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:19.36,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Despite how I look, I'm an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:23.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You look so young, \NI thought you were a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:27.01,Main Dialogue Top,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's a little too grown-up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:26.51,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:42.44,sign_18185_224_The_Hitotose_Tro,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The Hitotose Troupe's First Performance \N{\c&H231190&\fs28}A Strange Tale in a Strange Land \N{\fs22\c&H000000&}Starting today at 5:00 PM
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:42.44,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Please come watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:45.82,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Please come watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:48.83,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Please come watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:51.33,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Please come watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:54.62,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally show time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:56.41,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:12:59.59,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Everything went perfectly \Nin rehearsal, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:01.21,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:06.09,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.59,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:11.85,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,How've you been? I missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:14.42,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,How's school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:16.42,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown a bit taller, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.42,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:17.73,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Are you eating properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:18.70,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:20.61,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's a cute costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:22.28,sign_19196_242_Hinako__Wink_at_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako \N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Wink at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:22.28,sign_19196_243_Hinako__I_love_y,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako \N{\c&HFFFFFF&}I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:22.28,sign_19196_244_Hinako__Please_l,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako \N{\c&HF326E2&}Please look \Nat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:22.28,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some things to cheer you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:23.61,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it's enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:25.57,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,To cheer me on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:28.21,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it looks like there's some time \Nbefore the performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:28.62,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:33.41,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to check out Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:34.71,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of my things, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:36.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:38.77,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:41.75,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Break a leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:47.76,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom's so outgoing, unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:54.52,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Your mom went sightseeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.39,sign_20009_257_Hinako__Wave_at_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako \N{\c&H000000&}Wave at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.39,sign_20009_258_Hinako__Wink_at_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako \N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Wink at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.39,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:14:00.00,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,As your landlady, \NI was hoping to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:01.40,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:07.53,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,My mom has always been very active, \Noutgoing, and dynamic...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:10.53,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,She's the exact opposite of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:14.29,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, lots of kids are \Nnothing like their parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:17.79,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,My mom was a tea ceremony instructor,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:19.42,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,so she was strict about manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:22.68,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have the same taste \Nin clothes, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:24.18,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:28.43,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,My dad is a free spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:32.19,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,so I need to do a good job \Nrunning the shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:35.81,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,For you, that's a pretty \Nserious problem, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:39.27,Main Dialogue,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Amigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:42.27,sign_21082_273_The_Hitotose_Tro,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The Hitotose Troupe's First Performance \NA Strange Tale in a Strange Land \NStarting today at 5:00 PM \NLocation: Coffee Shop Hitotose
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:48.28,sign_21154_274_The_Hitotose_Tro,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The Hitotose Troupe's First Performance \N{\fs20\c&H4509C1&}A Strange Tale in a Strange Land \N{\fs16\c&H000000&}Today at 5:00 PM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:50.91,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Do come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:53.03,sign_21361_276_Reserved__Seat,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Reserved \NSeat
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:53.03,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Hitotose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:55.44,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Have you decided what you'd like to order?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:57.79,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,This is what we're recommending today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:00.79,Note,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HB8255A&}I ran after the white rabbit.\NI was so busy running after it, \NI somehow ended up upside down mid-air!\NI'm going to hit the ground!\NI closed my eyes tight and braced for impact.\NPoof\N\NHuh? It doesn't hurt...\NActually, it feels rather fluffy and soft.\NAnd more than anything...\N{\c&HBA2FE3&}"It's very warm..."\N{\c&HB8255A&}When I lowered my face into the fluff,\NI heard a mysterious voice.\N"Hey! Don't fluff me without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:00.79,Note - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HB8255A&}Startled by that voice, I looked up.\NI gently pet the warm, white object...\NThis fur is...\N{\c&HBA2FE3&}"Rabbit fur...?"\N{\c&HB8255A&}I heard the voice again.\N{\c&HEB8747&}"Come on! I have to hurry \Nto the Queen's palace!"\N\N{\c&HB8255A&}I still couldn't see who the voice belonged to,\Nbut it was probably this fluffy object.\N{\c&HBA2FE3&}"I'm sorry for fluffing you without permission.\NBut all I can see is your fur.\NI can't see the ground at all.\NI don't even know how to get down."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:12.05,sign_21742_281_Hitotose_Troupe_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hitotose Troupe \NFull House! \NWe're sorry. \NAll seats are filled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:10.21,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,The audience seats have really filled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:12.05,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:15.87,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm still okay right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:19.02,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,but I feel like I'll get nervous \Nwhen I see my mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:21.10,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:27.10,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be watching your performance \Nwith my mother today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:28.19,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.77,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I've seen her on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:32.42,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's a model...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:35.31,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in Sensei's family is famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:40.08,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan is already a scarecrow \Nafter seeing Sensei's mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:48.65,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you get nervous from \Nseeing someone else's mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:53.59,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I would recommend this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:57.60,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Will you flambé that with brandy, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:02.98,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry, but we don't serve \Nalcoholic beverages here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:05.47,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, breathe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.15,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,And out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:14.88,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It is kind of nerve-wracking to have \Nour families watching, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:18.99,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really like Parents' Day \Nat school when I was little, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:21.38,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,When I had to read out loud,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:21.38,Flashback Dialogue Top,KuinaFB,0000,0000,0000,,...held his umbrella over the fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:24.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd accidentally hold \Nmy textbook upside-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:25.76,Flashback Dialogue Top,KuinaFB,0000,0000,0000,,The fox looked at the old man in surprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:28.75,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I had the whole book \Nmemorized, so it was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:28.75,Flashback Dialogue Top,KuinaFB,0000,0000,0000,,then it barked happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:34.01,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I once forgot my lines \Nwhen I was on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:38.14,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I got through the rest \Nby ad-libbing, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:41.69,Flashback Dialogue,ChiakiFB,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right! If you keep \Nwishing and never give up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:43.52,Flashback Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,your dream will come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:46.65,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, because you're both geniuses...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:50.21,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, if you tell yourself \Nit's okay to mess up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.22,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,you won't get as nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:54.15,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:59.34,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I once messed up during a dance recital \Nand fell into the audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:03.04,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,but I got right back on the stage \Nand kept dancing until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:06.32,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Even I, the great Yua-sama, \Nmesses up sometimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.32,0:17:08.12,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,So don't feel bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:12.55,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:16.10,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have recovered \Nfrom something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:19.24,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Just imagining it makes me start shaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:22.93,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! It had the opposite effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:28.56,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,No, listen! What I'm saying is that \Nyou don't have to be afraid of messing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:29.63,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:33.19,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Just remember our play \Nat the culture festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:35.31,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The culture festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:37.95,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Remember the handkerchief?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:46.40,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, you're right. That \Nsomehow worked out okay, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:47.84,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:50.71,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,So you shouldn't be afraid \Nof making mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:56.14,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You succeeded in making \NHina-chan feel better!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:58.52,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I know I mess up all the time, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:04.72,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be there to help you, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:08.49,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's show your mom how cool you can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:10.61,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:16.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:19.24,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:21.12,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:24.13,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of all these girls \Nwho are supporting me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:26.87,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I have to make our \Nfirst performance a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:40.39,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I psyched myself up \Nbefore coming out here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:43.51,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako! Knock 'em dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.39,sign_26887_343_Hinako,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.51,sign_26911_344_Hinapon__LOVE,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hinapon \N{\c&H153436&}LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.76,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:47.89,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom's on your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:51.60,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,She really is making me nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:52.66,Main Dialogue Top,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Yay! Hinako! Go! Go! Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:56.76,Italics Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan's turning into a scarecrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.66,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:05.18,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Before we start, I'd like to say \Na few words as the shop owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:13.52,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Our shops, Used Bookstore Hitotose \Nand Coffee Shop Hitotose,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:15.20,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:16.92,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,produced this play for the \Nentertainment of customers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:15.92,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.92,sign_27715_362_1__Where_am_I___,Text,0000,0000,0000,,1) Where am I? \NWhat is this place I've come to? \N2)Why, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:21.93,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,visiting during the shopping \Ndistrict's stamp rally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:21.93,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Cue cards made with the shop's menu rolls...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:24.93,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,This is our theater troupe's \Nvery first performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:24.93,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan was up all night making them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:30.19,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,but we hope to earn your future support \Nas we move forward from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:30.19,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at Mayu-chan standing up as \Ntall as she can to show us our lines,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:31.98,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Also, our stamps for the stamp rally
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:31.98,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,and it'll soothe your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:38.37,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,can be collected at the table \Noutside the shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.79,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you meant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:36.07,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand still all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:40.45,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll move first, so you just follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:40.45,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,so please visit it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:44.87,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,They're doing all this just for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:53.15,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:56.46,Italics Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not standing on this stage alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:02.47,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:05.47,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place I've come to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:08.35,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:12.10,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to welcome you, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:16.36,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to a land so exciting, \Nyou'll be unable to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:20.11,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to a land so fun, \Nyou'll be unable to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:23.49,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Wonderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:26.44,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to show my mom
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:30.57,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,the best play I can put on, \Nwith my wonderful friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:35.12,Note,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&}When you can't do it right, lie down on your back and breathe.\NYou can tell that your stomach moves up and down,\Nrather than your lungs.\N\NThis is abdominal breathing!\NWhen you get the idea of how to do it lying down,\Ntry doing it again standing up!\N\N{\c&HFF0000&}Try at least 10 times a day\N\N{\c&HBA2FE3&}Point\N{\c&H000000&}With abdominal breathing, visualize that \Nyou're releasing your breath into your stomach\Nrather than your lungs when you breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:41.13,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:43.73,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the principal,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:47.51,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,but I put you all through so much trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:51.65,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,We got everything \Nback on track, so it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:54.52,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,The audience didn't seem to mind, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:56.20,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:20:59.02,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't moving at all in the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:01.78,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought you were playing \Na scarecrow or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:11.25,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But then you acted out your part\N until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:12.79,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You did so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.03,0:21:15.42,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're grown up, Hinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:17.67,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:19.52,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.52,0:21:21.71,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've put your mom's mind at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:24.86,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:26.59,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:32.35,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I came to Hitotose Manor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:36.35,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's time to catch \Nmy bullet train, so I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.61,0:21:37.30,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:40.30,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Girls, take care of Hinako for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:54.54,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,She's like a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:34.76,sign_33687_405_From_One_Year_to,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,6000)}From One Year to the Next
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.33,0:23:29.30,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of things have happened
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:31.53,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,since Hina-chan came to Hitotose Manor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:36.04,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I hope next year will be a good year, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:39.44,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "From One Year to the Next."
